Package org.web3d.x3d.sai

Interface SFVec4f

All Superinterfaces:
X3DField
All Known Implementing Classes:
SFVec4fObject
public interface SFVec4f
extends X3DField
SFVec4f is a 4-tuple set of single-precision floating-point values, specifying a 3D homogeneous vector. Warning: comma characters in attribute values do not pass strict XML validation.


Package hint: This interface is defined by the X3D Java Language Binding Specification for the Scene Authoring Interface (SAI).
See Also:
SAI Java Specification: B.4.47, SAI Abstract Specification: 5.2.15 SAIFieldType, X3D Abstract Specification: 5.3.21 SFVec4f and MFVec4f, X3D Tooltips, X3D Tooltips: field, X3D Tooltips: fieldValue, X3D Scene Authoring Hints
